	<p pid="b.138.1/1">asked Her Majesty's Government:</p>
	<p pid="b.138.1/2" qnum="0">[<i>An incomplete version of the following Written Answer was received and published on 10 October</i>.]</p>
	<p pid="b.138.1/3" qnum="1601">For each year since 1998, how much compensation has been paid to civilians in South Armagh as a result of security forces' alleged activities in the area. [HL</p>
